data.description: Fantastic two-story home nestled in the highly sought out neighborhood of Longs Creek. This home features a galley kitchen, a large family/living room with a cozy fireplace, 4 bedrooms, and a 2 car garage. Large master retreat with a huge walk-in closet. Entertainers dream backyard with a spacious deck, nice sized yard, plenty of shade by mature trees, and is all surrounded by a privacy fence. Make it your home today!
